}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== .. there would appear to be different revisions of this device with differing internals. The '''Amazon''' entry specifies the device uses a '''Terminus''' chipset.
The S/N for the device populating this entry is '''21928B090102566'''. :The '''NEC''' hub ICs marked with "NEC", 720114", and "821EA".
This hub presents itself to the host system as two 0409:005a devices.
The power adapter distributed with the device would appear to be an '''unbranded''' SPS12-5.0-2000 (100-240VAC [50-60Hz] 0.5A -> 5.0V 2.0A), which is indicated to be manufactured in China.
